-- Nine Eni Managers Investigated by Italian Financial Police in Tax Probe
-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 2010-12-20T23:26:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-20/nine-eni-managers-investigated-by-italian-financial-police-in-tax-probe.html
Nine Eni SpA managers have been
investigated by financial police in Milan in a probe concerning
accusations about unpaid taxes totaling 1.7 billion euros ($2.2
billion), company spokesman Gianni di Giovanni said by telephone
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Livesey at 
 blivesey@bloomberg.net  